<h1>RESPECT OTHERS' COMMENTS</h1>
<p>"Let not all be spokesmen at once; but let one speak at a time and let all listen unto his sayings, that when all have spoken that all may be edified of all." (Doctrine &amp; Covenants 88:122)</p>
<p>The gospel teaches us to always respect and be kind to others. That includes the learning process. Realize that we are all on different planes of learning &mdash; some are on a plane below and some above. Treat people with respect and a comfortable atmosphere will be sustained where learning can thrive.</p>
